  "774059": {"id":"774059","categorySlug":"automation-technology-industrial-communication-pilz>safety-relay","translations":{"ar":{"keys":[{"key":"شرح المنتج","value":")، المدخلات: توصيل أحادي القناة (1 قناة) المخارج: 2 عادة مفتوحة (N/O) تشغيل تلقائي / يدوي جهد التغذية: 24 فولت AC/DC العرض: 22.5 مم أطراف توصيل لولبية مدمجة مراقبة الإيقاف الطارئ (E-STOP) أبواب الأمان."},{"key":"حالة المنتج","value":"جديد بالكرتون"},{"key":"متوفر في المخزون","value":"متوفر في المخزون"},{"key":"جاهز للشحن الفوري","value":"✔️"},{"key":"يشمل ضمان متجر","value":"🟢"}]},"en":{"keys":[{"key":"product description","value":"Safety relay (standalone), inputs: 1-channel wiring, outputs: 2 N/O, automatic/manual start, UB 24 V AC/DC, width: 22.5 mm, screw terminals integrated, monitoring of E-STOP, safety gates."},{"key":"Product Condition","value":"New in Box "},{"key":"Stock Status","value":"✅"},{"key":"Available for Immediate Shipment","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Covered by Store Warranty","value":"🟢"}]},"tr":{"keys":[{"key":"ürün açıklaması","value":"Emniyet rölesi (bağımsız), girişler: 1 kanallı kablolama, çıkışlar: 2 normalde açık (N/O), otomatik/manuel başlatma, UB 24 V AC/DC, genişlik: 22,5 mm, entegre vidalı terminaller, acil durdurma (E-STOP) izleme, emniyet kapıları."},{"key":"Ürün durumu","value":"Sıfır Kutusunda "},{"key":"Stok Durumu","value":"✅"},{"key":"Hemen Sevkiyata Hazır","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Mağaza Garantisi Kapsamında","value":"🟢"}]}},"i18n":{"ar":{},"en":{},"tr":{}},"unCategorySlug":"","price":"contact"},
  "777601": {"id":"777601","categorySlug":"automation-technology-industrial-communication-pilz>safety-relay","translations":{"ar":{"keys":[{"key":"شرح المنتج","value":"مرحل أمان (مستقل)،\nالمدخلات: توصيل بقناة واحدة أو قناتين مع/بدون كشف القصر بين نقاط التلامس\nالمخارج: 2 عادة مفتوحة (N/O)، و1 عادة مفتوحة مع تأخير زمني (N/Ot-d)\nتشغيل تلقائي / تشغيل مع مراقبة\nجهد التغذية: 24 فولت تيار مستمر (24 V DC)\nالعرض: 22.5 مم\nأطراف توصيل لولبية قابلة للتركيب\nمراقبة الإيقاف الطارئ (E-STOP)، بوابات الأمان، ستارة الضوء\nزمن التحرير: 0.1 – 3 ثوانٍ."},{"key":"حالة المنتج","value":"جديد بالكرتون"},{"key":"متوفر في المخزون","value":"متوفر في المخزون"},{"key":"جاهز للشحن الفوري","value":"✔️"},{"key":"يشمل ضمان متجر","value":"🟢"}]},"en":{"keys":[{"key":"product description","value":"Safety relay (standalone), inputs: 1/2-channel wiring with/without detection of shorts across contacts, outputs: 2 N/O, 1 N/Ot-d, automatic/monitored start, UB = 24 V DC, width: 22.5 mm, plug-in screw terminals, monitoring of E-STOP, safety gates, light curtain, release time 0.1 - 3 s."},{"key":"Product Condition","value":"New in Box "},{"key":"Stock Status","value":"✅"},{"key":"Available for Immediate Shipment","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Covered by Store Warranty","value":"🟢"}]},"tr":{"keys":[{"key":"ürün açıklaması","value":"Emniyet rölesi (bağımsız), girişler: kontaklar arası kısa devre algılamalı/algılamasız 1/2 kanallı kablolama, çıkışlar: 2 normalde açık (N/O), 1 normalde açık (N/Ot-d), otomatik/izlemeli başlatma, UB = 24 V DC, genişlik: 22,5 mm, takılabilir vidalı terminaller, acil durdurma (E-STOP) izleme, emniyet kapıları, ışık perdesi, serbest bırakma süresi 0,1 - 3 s."},{"key":"Ürün durumu","value":"Sıfır Kutusunda "},{"key":"Stok Durumu","value":"✅"},{"key":"Hemen Sevkiyata Hazır","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Mağaza Garantisi Kapsamında","value":"🟢"}]}},"i18n":{"ar":{},"en":{},"tr":{}},"unCategorySlug":"","price":"contact"},
