  "6GK5907-8UA00-0AA0": {"id":"6GK5907-8UA00-0AA0","categorySlug":"automation-technology-industrial-ethernet>plug-in-transceivers-for-scalance","translations":{"ar":{"keys":[{"key":"شرح المنتج","value":"SCALANCE CLP 2 GB W700 AP iFeatures. وسيط تخزين بيانات قابل للإزالة لتفعيل iFeatures والوظائف الإضافية في نقاط الوصول والعملاء من SCALANCE W.  يمكن استخدامه لاستبدال الجهاز بسهولة في حال حدوث عطل، ولتخزين بيانات التهيئة والبرامج الثابتة (Firmware).  يمكن استخدامه في المنتجات التالية المزودة بفتحة CLP: SCALANCE W700 Wi-Fi 5 و Wi-Fi 6."},{"key":"حالة المنتج","value":"جديد بالكرتون"},{"key":"متوفر في المخزون","value":"✅"},{"key":"جاهز للشحن الفوري","value":"✔️"},{"key":"يشمل ضمان متجر","value":"🟢"}]},"en":{"keys":[{"key":"product description","value":"SCALANCE CLP 2 GB W700 AP iFeatures. removable data storage medium for activating iFeatures and supplementary functions in SCALANCE W access points and clients. can be used for easy device replacement in case of failure, for recording configuration data, and firmware, can be used in the following products with CLP slot: SCALANCE W700 Wi-Fi 5 and Wi-Fi 6."},{"key":"Product Condition","value":"New in Box "},{"key":"Stock Status","value":"✅"},{"key":"Available for Immediate Shipment","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Covered by Store Warranty","value":"🟢"}]},"tr":{"keys":[{"key":"ürün açıklaması","value":"SCALANCE CLP 2 GB W700 AP iFeatures. SCALANCE W erişim noktaları ve istemcilerinde iFeatures ve ek fonksiyonları etkinleştirmek için çıkarılabilir veri depolama ortamı.  Arıza durumunda kolay cihaz değişimi için, konfigürasyon verilerinin ve firmware’in kaydedilmesi amacıyla kullanılabilir.  CLP yuvasına sahip aşağıdaki ürünlerde kullanılabilir: SCALANCE W700 Wi-Fi 5 ve Wi-Fi 6."},{"key":"Ürün durumu","value":"Sıfır Kutusunda "},{"key":"Stok Durumu","value":"✅"},{"key":"Hemen Sevkiyata Hazır","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Mağaza Garantisi Kapsamında","value":"🟢"}]}},"i18n":{"ar":{},"en":{},"tr":{}},"unCategorySlug":"","price":"contact"},
  "6GK1900-0UB00-0AA0": {"id":"6GK1900-0UB00-0AA0","categorySlug":"automation-technology-industrial-ethernet>plug-in-transceivers-for-scalance","translations":{"ar":{"keys":[{"key":"شرح المنتج","value":"SCALANCE CLP 2 GB وسيط تخزين بيانات قابل للإزالة لاستبدال الجهاز بسهولة في حال حدوث عطل، ولتخزين بيانات التهيئة.  يمكن استخدامه في المنتجات التالية المزودة بفتحة CLP."},{"key":"حالة المنتج","value":"جديد بالكرتون"},{"key":"متوفر في المخزون","value":"✅"},{"key":"جاهز للشحن الفوري","value":"✔️"},{"key":"يشمل ضمان متجر","value":"🟢"}]},"en":{"keys":[{"key":"product description","value":"SCALANCE CLP 2 GB removable data storage medium for simple device replacement in case of failure, for recording configuration data, can be used in the following products with CLP slot"},{"key":"Product Condition","value":"New in Box "},{"key":"Stock Status","value":"✅"},{"key":"Available for Immediate Shipment","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Covered by Store Warranty","value":"🟢"}]},"tr":{"keys":[{"key":"ürün açıklaması","value":"SCALANCE CLP 2 GB Arıza durumunda kolay cihaz değişimi için ve konfigürasyon verilerinin kaydedilmesi amacıyla kullanılan çıkarılabilir veri depolama ortamı.  CLP yuvasına sahip aşağıdaki ürünlerde kullanılabilir."},{"key":"Ürün durumu","value":"Sıfır Kutusunda "},{"key":"Stok Durumu","value":"✅"},{"key":"Hemen Sevkiyata Hazır","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Mağaza Garantisi Kapsamında","value":"🟢"}]}},"i18n":{"ar":{},"en":{},"tr":{}},"unCategorySlug":"","price":"contact"},
