  "PXI-7344": {"id":"PXI-7344","categorySlug":"automation-technology-national-instruments>pxi-embedded-controller","translations":{"ar":{"keys":[{"key":"شرح المنتج","value":"السلسلة: NI-73xx Series النوع: وحدة تحكم حركة Stepper/Servo Motion Controller الإدخال/الإخراج الرقمي: 4 منافذ، كل منفذ 8-بت دقة الإدخال: 12 بت عدد المحاور: 4 محاور نطاق جهد الإدخال/الإخراج الرقمي: 0 إلى 5 فولت مصادر ساعة الإدخال/الإخراج الرقمي: داخلية أو خارجية استهلاك الطاقة: 5.7 واط كحد أقصى نطاق درجة حرارة التشغيل: 0°C إلى 55°C نطاق درجة حرارة التخزين: –20°C إلى 70°C موصلات الإدخال/الإخراج: موصلان أنثيان 68-Pin عالي الكثافة VHDCI الأبعاد: 6.3 × 3.9 بوصة (16 × 10 سم) بدون الموصلات الضمان:  دليل PXI-7344: دليل المستخدم ودليل الصيانة متاحان للتنزيل"},{"key":"حالة المنتج","value":"جديد"},{"key":"متوفر في المخزون","value":"✅"},{"key":"جاهز للشحن الفوري","value":"✔️"},{"key":"يشمل ضمان متجر","value":"🟢"}]},"en":{"keys":[{"key":"product description","value":"Seri: NI-73xx Serisi Tip: Stepper/Servo Motion Controller Modülü Dijital G/Ç: 4 adet 8-bit port Giriş çözünürlüğü: 12 bit Eksen sayısı: 4 eksen Dijital G/Ç voltaj aralığı: 0 – 5 V Dijital G/Ç saat kaynakları: Dahili veya harici Güç tüketimi: Maksimum 5.7 W Çalışma sıcaklığı aralığı: 0°C – 55°C Depolama sıcaklığı aralığı: –20°C – 70°C G/Ç konnektörleri: 2 adet dişi 68-Pin yüksek yoğunluklu VHDCI Boyutlar: 6.3 × 3.9 inç (16 × 10 cm) konnektörler hariç PXI-7344 Kılavuzu: Kullanım ve bakım kılavuzu indirilebilir"},{"key":"Product Condition","value":"New"},{"key":"Stock Status","value":"✅"},{"key":"Available for Immediate Shipment","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Covered by Store Warranty","value":"🟢"}]},"tr":{"keys":[{"key":"ürün açıklaması","value":"Series: NI-73xx Series Type: Stepper/Servo Motion Controller Module Digital I/O: 4, 8-Bit Ports Input Resolution: 12 Bits Axes: 4 Digital I/O Voltage Range: 0 to 5 V Digital I/O Clock Sources: Internal or External Power Consumption: 5.7 W Maximum Operating Temperature Range: 0 °C to 55 °C Storage Temperature Range: –20 °C to 70 °C I/O Connectors: Two Female 68-Pin High-Density VHDCI Dimensions: 6.3 × 3.9 in. (16 × 10 cm) without connectors  PXI-7344 Manual: User Manual and Maintenance Manual Available for Download"},{"key":"Ürün durumu","value":"Sıfır"},{"key":"Stok Durumu","value":"✅"},{"key":"Hemen Sevkiyata Hazır","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Mağaza Garantisi Kapsamında","value":"🟢"}]}},"i18n":{"ar":{},"en":{},"tr":{}},"unCategorySlug":"","price":"contact"},
  "PXI-4472": {"id":"PXI-4472","categorySlug":"automation-technology-national-instruments>pxi-embedded-controller","translations":{"ar":{"keys":[{"key":"شرح المنتج","value":"الميزات: دقة 24 بت نطاق ديناميكي 110 ديسيبل أقصى معدل أخذ عينات 102.4 كيلوعينة/ثانية (kS/s) عرض نطاق خالٍ من التمويه 45 كيلوهرتز نطاق الجهد ±10 فولت اقتران AC/DC"},{"key":"حالة المنتج","value":"جديد بالكرتون"},{"key":"متوفر في المخزون","value":"✅"},{"key":"جاهز للشحن الفوري","value":"✔️"},{"key":"يشمل ضمان متجر","value":"🟢"}]},"en":{"keys":[{"key":"product description","value":"Özellikler: 24-Bit çözünürlük 110 dB dinamik aralık Maksimum örnekleme hızı 102.4 kS/s 45 kHz alias-free bant genişliği ±10 V ölçüm aralığı AC/DC kuplaj"},{"key":"Product Condition","value":"New in Box "},{"key":"Stock Status","value":"✅"},{"key":"Available for Immediate Shipment","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Covered by Store Warranty","value":"🟢"}]},"tr":{"keys":[{"key":"ürün açıklaması","value":"Features: 24-Bit Resolution 110 dB Dynamic Range 102.4 kS/s Maximum Sampling Rate 45 kHz Alias-Free Bandwidth ±10 V Range AC/DC Coupling"},{"key":"Ürün durumu","value":"Sıfır Kutusunda "},{"key":"Stok Durumu","value":"✅"},{"key":"Hemen Sevkiyata Hazır","value":"✔️"},{"key":"Mağaza Garantisi Kapsamında","value":"🟢"}]}},"i18n":{"ar":{},"en":{},"tr":{}},"unCategorySlug":"","price":"contact"},
